# Summary
This documentation page describes how to integrate Amplitude with Hotjar using a custom Destination Plugin that forwards Amplitude events to Hotjar's tracking system, enabling combined analytics and user experience insights by implementing the Hotjar browser tracking code within Amplitude's SDK plugin architecture.

